{"type": "article", "id": 13477, "title": "谁说运动场不能精致一点？", "description": "体育项目将过去和现在连接起来。 ", "date": "2015-08-13T17:10:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3313, "name": "洛杉矶"}, {"id": 14498, "name": "体育场改造"}, {"id": 14499, "name": "加利福尼亚"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143305mJ9hyK7Y5jzA0bi4.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t在加利福尼亚的洛杉矶，有个叫作 Santa Anita Race Track 的老旧运动场，它始建于 1934 年，到今天为止，已经历 80 余年风雨了。<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/back-to-the-future-an-old-californian-race-track-gets-a-contemporary-makeover/9426#125416\" target=\"_blank\">最近一个叫作 Studio Antares 的工作室改建了它</a>，建筑师们给老旧的看台换上了皮座椅和木地板，旧看台散发出了仿古气息。\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143302EJijoRB6Y9Vygrqc.jpg\" title=\"长凳让人想起传统俱乐部套房中的椅子\" alt=\"长凳让人想起传统俱乐部套房中的椅子\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">长凳让人想起传统俱乐部套房中的椅子\r\n</div>\r\n<span> \r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061433020D7FAEhvd6HfnoTB.jpg\" title=\"室内设计都是复古风格\" alt=\"室内设计都是复古风格\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>室内是复古风格</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143302C4KFl8eG5gaknHx6.jpg\" title=\"内室\" alt=\"内室\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>木地板和走廊里的长凳</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061433038miNHAXI5sUOSTEh.jpg\" title=\"看台\" alt=\"看台\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>看台</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t在内室，设计师选用了深色的地板、真皮座椅和大型黑白壁画，小装饰则使用了俏皮的亮色，避免沉闷。<span>设计师在接受采访时说，改建的目标是创造一种新旧并存的环境，而体育项目能将体育场的过去和现在连接起来。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143303X1M9lZB5QcEiozIb.jpg\" title=\"内室设计\" alt=\"内室设计\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内室制造出了轻松惬意的感觉</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143304fzAIUwtBFC56KlHn.jpg\" title=\"远处的山脉若隐若现\" alt=\"远处的山脉若隐若现\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>远处的山脉若隐若现</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143305vmOUckVPtQ809NLT.jpg\" title=\"看来橙色和绿色是绝配\" alt=\"看来橙色和绿色是绝配\" data-ratio=\"0.6125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>看来橙色和绿色挺搭</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><em><a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/architecture/back-to-the-future-an-old-californian-race-track-gets-a-contemporary-makeover/9426#125414\" target=\"_blank\">wallpaper</a></em>\r\n</p>\r\n</span>\n\n\n"}